com.odesk.agora.mercury.consumer

Class TypedMessage<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.odesk.agora.mercury.MercuryMessage
      • com.odesk.agora.mercury.consumer.TypedMessage<T>

  • public class TypedMessage<T>
extends MercuryMessage
    Created by Dmitry Solovyov on 01/20/2016.

    Type-safe wrapper for Mercury message containing a deserialized version of MercuryMessage.serializedPayload. Should not be instantiated directly. The instances are created on the fly by the deserializing consumer registered with MercuryConsumers.setDeserializingConsumer(String, MercuryConsumers.DeserializerForClass, Consumer) or MercuryConsumers.setTypedConsumer(String, Class, Consumer).
